name: Cinderella Divine Sleeveless Mermaid Wedding Gown
description: This elegant dress, made with premium materials, shines out with a stunning confection of lace, embellishments, and tulle fabric. Both romantic and conventional brides looking for a touch of sophistication and flawless taste will love this off the shoulder wedding dress!

name: Leon Long Wedding Dress Bridal
description: Discover the dream of your perfect wedding dress at Gowny. This gorgeous long wedding dress features a puff sleeves worthy of medieval princess. A-line dress with elongated back skirt design. This Andrea & Leo wedding dress is a perfect choice for both romantic and elegant brides who desire a hint of class with perfect style!

name: Andrea Long Off Shoulder Wedding Dress Bridal
description: This whimsical long wedding dress features an off shoulder sweetheart neckline. A-line dress, decorated with lace appliques.

name: CÉLINE Sparkling Tulle Wedding Dress
description: CÉLINE is a sparkling A-line wedding dress with a unique sculpted scoop neckline on multiple layers of lace and tulle, as well as sweet, detachable off-the-shoulder tulle sleeves. The glimmering floral lace is delicately placed on the bodice and cascades down to the soft tulle skirt featuring a sexy slit. Have all your wedding guests’ jaws drop when they see the stunning exposed illusion corset back and the impeccable sculpted train.

name: Cinderella Divine Long A-line Bridal Gown
description: This gorgeous long bridal dress features a strapless sweetheart neckline. Layered tulle skirt with slit, lace applique over structured bodice.

name: Long Formal Mermaid Style Wedding Gown
description: This gorgeous mermaid dress features a deep v-neckline with mesh inset. Fitted mermaid style decorated with sparkling rhinestones. Made from high quality and comfortable materials, the fit and design will take your breath away.

name: Janet Wedding Dress
description: Full of romance and whimsy, our Janet designer wedding dress features a beautiful boned bodice with a sweetheart neckline in lovely Chantilly lace, all adorned with floral crystal beaded embroidery. The A-line tulle gown has a cloud-like effect and delicately floats off the body to a sweet lace-trimmed train. Pair the dress with detachable pouf sleeves for a more playful look. Shown in Ivory/Honey.

name: Maxine Wedding Dress
description: Our Maxine wedding dress gives you a one-of-a-kind wedding day look. The mini dress features stunning frosted, three-dimensional lace appliqués over shimmering sparkle tulle with a sultry, plunging sweetheart neckline. The detachable tulle overskirt adds volume and drama, serving two looks in one, perfect for transitioning from ceremony to reception, while detachable bell sleeves add a boho flair.

name: Melina Wedding Dress
description: Dramatic texture makes our Melina designer wedding dress a stand out. The straight neck, strapless bodice has boning to give you structure and shape, enhancing the look of a narrow waist. Blingy crystal beading on pattern sequin tulle over sparkle tulle gives the bodice an unreal shimmer, especially when paired with the over-the-top ruffled organza ball gown skirt.

name: Mckenna Wedding Dress
description: An instant classic, our Mckenna designer wedding dress is an understated ball gown in radiant Diamantina satin. The strapless, sweetheart bodice features contoured seaming, that helps to lengthen the body, and a billowing A-line skirt. The peplum on the back is a vintage touch that we’re sure our brides will love.

name: Maisie Wedding Dress
description: Our Maisie designer wedding dress is a whimsical A-line with enchanting details. The sweetheart bodice features stunning frosted embroidered appliqués over romantic Chantilly lace, with angled boning to give you the look of a narrow waist. The effortless tulle skirt floats off the body, featuring a front skirt slit for added movement, and a lovely lace-trimmed train. Detachable long pouf sleeves with ruched cuff at the wrist add to the fairytale feeling of the gown.

name: Lucy Wedding Dress
description: Our Lucy designer wedding dress combines modern design with vintage inspiration. Featuring a modest bateau bodice with contoured seams to define your figure on the ball gown silhouette. The pleated satin skirt feels classic and the buttons down to the hemline are a timeless touch, but our favorite part is the satin organza bishop sleeves with a cuff at the wrist.

name: Marjorie Wedding Dress
description: Our Marjorie designer wedding dress is a dramatic ball gown with simple details. The silky Larissa satin gown has a strapless, sweetheart bodice with textural seams for added dimension. The pleated A-line skirt is voluminous, with a grand feel and a daring skirt slit for a modern design element. Buttons down to the hem are a timeless touch making this a truly classic ball gown.

name: Janine Wedding Dress
description: Get all the fairytale feels with our Janine designer wedding dress. The sheer corset bodice dazzles with intricate beading and a sultry center plunge detail that leads to gorgeous triple beaded straps. The glimmering glitter tulle skirt is fabulously flounced with horsehair edging to define each layer for a textured and dramatic look.

name: Jeanette Wedding Dress
description: Our Jeanette designer wedding dress serves you the full fairytale fantasy with botanical-inspired frosted embroidered lace on an effortless A-line silhouette. The tulle looks ethereal as it floats off the body, while the structured strapless bodice, with peek-a-boo detail, gives the dress an edge. Detachable draped off-the-shoulder bishop sleeves add to the whimsy of the gown.

name: Josefina Wedding Dress
description: If you want drama and glamour, look no further than our Josefina designer wedding dress. The over-the-top ball gown features a delicately draped bodice with romantic sweetheart neckline and a matching detachable tie-back stole. The ruffled tulle skirt creates fabulous texture with a subtle, swirling floral motif for a gown that will leave guests gasping as you walk down the aisle.

name: Farrah Wedding Dress
description: Your fairytale bridal dreams come true in our Farrah designer wedding dress. This beautiful ball gown features a decadent mix of ivy-inspired lace and frosted, three-dimensional floral appliqués. The romantic off-the-shoulder bodice is enhanced with illusion details, like the beautiful sheer back.

name: Fausta Wedding Dress
description: Our Fausta designer wedding dress is here to sweep you off your feet. The beautiful ball gown features a Chantilly lace bodice, with a sweetheart neckline, adorned in crystal beaded, three-dimensional floral embroidery. The fantasy continues with a full organza ball gown skirt and sparkling crystal buttons lining down to the horsehair edged hem. Detachable tie bow sleeves add a touch of whimsy to the dress.

name: Filomena Wedding Dress
description: The ultimate fairytale dress, our Filomena designer wedding dress is flirty and fanciful. The sparkle tulle A-line ball gown features a structured scoop neckline on a sheer corset bodice adorned in crystal beaded, three-dimensional lace appliqués. A lace-up corset back and detachable bishop sleeves that cinch at the wrist add to the whimsical fantasy.

name: Megan Wedding Dress
description: Our Megan designer wedding dress is a fierce fit and flare with romantic details. The sheer bodice has a strapless, sweetheart neckline with boning for structure and support. Stunning crystal beaded embroidered lace appliqués over Chantilly lace create a beautiful layered lace effect. Style the dress with our Tulle Overskirt with Crystal Beaded Waistband for a fuller silhouette, giving you two looks in one.
